%C - This is a QNX/Photon Application.
%C [options]

Options:
  -s server     Server path or device name

Msg Options:
  -v            add a level of verbosity
  -o filename   Write messages to specified filename
  -m            Write to memo [default]
  -V            Write to stderr
  
PhRTG Options:
  -P path       Specify default path for MLF variables
  -C node       Specify node name for command server

Examples:
%C -s photon_s
  Run using Photon server on /dev/photon_s

%C -s /net/magenta/dev/photon
  Run using Photon server on node "/net/magenta"

%C -x10 -y10 -h200 -w300
  Run at initial position 10,10 with initial dimension of 200x300.
